@startuml US_4.1.2_SSD
autonumber

actor "Logistics\nOperator" as Operator
participant ":System" as System

== Select Date ==
activate Operator
Operator -> System: Acede à secção "Operation Planning"
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta interface de planeamento
deactivate System
Operator -> System: Seleciona data no calendário
activate System
System --> Operator: Confirma seleção de data
deactivate System

== Select Algorithm ==
Operator -> System: Seleciona algoritmo de scheduling
activate System
System --> Operator: Confirma seleção do algoritmo
deactivate System

== Generate Plans ==
Operator -> System: Clica em "Generate Plans"
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta planos de operação gerados
deactivate System

== Review Plans ==
Operator -> System: Revê lista de planos gerados
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta detalhes dos planos
deactivate System

== Save Plans ==
Operator -> System: Clica em "Save Plans"
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta confirmação de gravação
deactivate System
deactivate Operator

@enduml
